VALUES (1, 'GHST', 6, NULL, 'Mining ghouls', 'Commuters near Black Mountain in Kentucky are seeing luminescent and emaciated figures walking by the roads near old mining sites. Sometimes the figures walkk other times just standing. Cannot make out their eyes but based on their bodies it seems they''re always facing the mountain. People have been trying to take pictures but claim their phones/cameras always fail during photography. Elders from nearby communities call them the "ones that never left".', 'NORMAL', 'SUBMITTED', ARRAY[6,8], ARRAY[8], '2024-12-08T10:23:00', '2024-12-13T16:30:00', 'POINT(36.9084 -82.8896)', NEXTVAL('custom_seq'));
VALUES (2, 'CRPTD', 5, NULL, 'Finland - highland strangeness', 'Multiple herders reported glimpses of a massive Forest Reindeer with shimmering, water-like hides when walking into moonlight. No tracks left behind in fresh snow and the herders say the reindeer ''speak'' in human voices before vanishing. Field cameras placed along migration routes have so far captured a cold, metallic outline where their image should be.', 'NORMAL', 'SUBMITTED', ARRAY[2,5], ARRAY[1], '2024-12-10T17:56:00', '2024-12-17T13:22:00', 'POINT(64.8789 27.8493)', NEXTVAL('custom_seq'));
VALUES (1, 'GHST', 4, NULL, 'Concerning shadows in manor house windows', 'Windows at an manor house outside of the abandoned town of Greenwater, California display menacing-looking shadows with an orange-red glow around them. Unclear if this is a hoax by pranksters but highly suspected.', 'NORMAL', 'SUBMITTED', ARRAY[3,4,1,9], ARRAY[1,9], '2024-12-12T14:23:00', '2024-12-12T14:23:00', 'POINT(36.1794 -116.6163)', NEXTVAL('custom_seq'));
VALUES (1, 'GHST', 4, NULL, 'Convoy of ghost cars with bizarre-looking occupants', 'Late-night drivers overtaken by a convoy of vintage black pick-ups with no license plates. Witnesses claim the drivers'' faces appeared melted, like wax figures in the sun. State troopers found fresh tire tracks — but no vehicles.', 'NORMAL', 'SUBMITTED', ARRAY[4,6,8,9], ARRAY[6,8], '2024-12-12T14:23:00', '2024-12-12T14:23:00', NULL, NEXTVAL('custom_seq'));
