VALUES (3, 'SHFTR', 2, 2, 'Suspicious tree breaks in Fraser Valley, plus aggressive hollering and near-miss attacks on hikers', 'Clean mid-height tree breaks in the Harrison Hot Springs area. Large coniferous trees >2 feet in diameter affected. Locals and visiting hikers also reporting ''primal, ape-like shouting'' around Echo Island, and large rocks thrown in their direction when walking near Hicks Lake. People are staying away from the area in the meantime.', 'MINOR', 'SUBMITTED', ARRAY[2,1], ARRAY[1], '2025-01-03T22:54:00', '2025-01-10T08:13:00', 'POINT(49.029 -122.2854)', NEXTVAL('custom_seq'));
